name: Gwan-c-tools
body:
#Ronaldo Barbachano
##http://doinglines.com
##4-9-2012

This repository houses various scripts/examples I have written in C that demonstrate core functionality in G-WAN.
Please see individual files in csp for comments. Other gwan resources may follow inside of this repository, as there
does not seem to be any resources/communities or even forums.

For More information about G-WAN visit http://gwan.ch
tagline: Scripts, and examples for G-WAN, written in C.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
